author: Climate Town
description:
TV is fun, but don't take your climate policy suggestions from a Billy Bob Thornton monologue. We did a whole breakdown on why the show Landman is maybe a bit bias, but here was my personal favorite anti-wind argument.

Check out the whole video here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wBC_bug5DIQ
title: The Dumbest Anti-Wind Propaganda On Television
